<h2>Horse Excursions in Lapland</h2>
<p><img src="/media/13050888/filzmoos-4.jpg" alt="HorseDrawn" data-udi="umb://media/ed0e8b0860a147e7b87cbdcf14b8dac9" /></p>
<p>Enjoying a horse back-ride (or perhaps a sleigh ride) is a gentle way to take in your surroundings whilst in Lapland. The local horses to Lapland are strong and loving creatures, who wouldn’t turn their nose up at a little snack if offered. Together, you and the horses can take a memorable ride around the local forests and breathe in the wonderfully fresh air. </p>
<p>You can either opt to go for a horse ride, or if you would prefer to huddle up warmly as a family, you can enjoy a sleigh ride instead. </p>
<h3>Horse winter excursion options available per resort:</h3>
