<div class="g12">
<div class="white_box_shadow"><img src="/media/13073467/horse-riding.jpeg" alt="horseriding" data-udi="umb://media/6b0a50878e1b471985537f6daa3e1db8" /><br />
<h3>What’s included in a Horse excursion: </h3>
<p>Enjoy the winter magic whilst riding along snowy forest trails. With a rose tinted sky being seen through the snow-laden trees, you will get the feeling of an enchanted journey on horseback.</p>
<p>A perfect experience for both beginner and experienced riders, you will warm up after your hack with a hot drink and cookie. You may also choose to sit back and relax in a one horse open sleigh under the starry night sky, being in <a data-udi="umb://document/9933a896cd594899ac7150e009590145" href="/{localLink:umb://document/9933a896cd594899ac7150e009590145}" title="Northern Lights Adventures" data-anchor="#">search of the Northern Lights</a>.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g12">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<p><img src="/media/13050726/04-bkk.jpg" alt="hoseinsnow" data-udi="umb://media/8d6467b8df60441aaf04aae57aa17edc" /></p>
<h3>How to book your Horse excursion:<span style="font-weight: 400;"> </span></h3>
<p><span>You can add excursions to your holiday package via your '<a href="https://my.inghams.co.uk/login">My Booking</a>' portal or you can speak to a member of our UK based team on <span class="InfinityNumber">01483 791 111.</span></span></p>
<p><strong>Please note:</strong> Available in Levi only. Suitable for beginners. Advanced riders will have their own group. Children under 9 yrs must be experienced. Children must be accompanied by an adult 18 years and over.</p>
<p>• Beginner horse riding experience available for adults and children (9-12 years old), no experience required.<br />• Intermediate horse-riding experience available for adults and children (7 – 12 years old), previous experience required.</p>
</div>
</div>
